An e-commerce business allowing payments and money transfers to be made from through the Internet.EUR).

TransferWise can send funds from U.K. bank account to a Eur bank account and will perform the currency conversion at mid-market rates.  

The service is available for sending from an individual account or from a business account.

##Fees

There is a 1 GBP fee per transfer.

